content: Just a quick message to convey my thanks to everyone that has contributed to PhysLean during 2025. Whether that be directly contributing to the code-base, messaging on this Zulip, coming along to PhysLean cafes, or giving me private words of advice or encouragement. This project would not have evolved in the same way without each of these contributions, and if there was a way I could further express my gratitude then I would.
